author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
This is the second part of my foray into the artist that is Benson Boone. I've reviewed one of his songs before, but my Producer wanted me to listen to his latest work, "Mystical, Magical". Maybe I'd done something to upset her. It's too 'Pop' for my liking, but it reminded me of the classic 80's hit, "Physical". I later discovered that its writers were credited on this. Who knew? Well, I do now. 

To hear the whole track, visit: https://youtu.be/U8QhB8_0t2g?si=6ITUiROUtU8gJK--

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

title: Mystical, Magical? No, Sickly Sweet.
